    - "any proprietary source"
  notes:
    - "Wave 653 (uu3091): __hash__, __eq__, __bool__ dict-presence checks for uuid.UUID."
    - "uuid.UUID is a value type and defines both __hash__ and __eq__ in its __dict__."
    - "uuid.UUID does not define __bool__ in its __dict__; truthiness falls back to the default."
    - "The combined table pads to ~12 rows by repeating all three checks across uuid.UUID."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
error_model: python_exceptions

